\p{This site is a "forest" created using [Forester](https://www.forester-notes.org). To navigate the forest you can click headings to collapse or expand notes, or click on the ID to open the standalone note. It is also possible to search the forest by pressing \<html:kbd>{\<html:kbd>{Ctrl}+\<html:kbd>{K}}. This is forest is still in its infancy, in it I want to write about what I am doing while I'm unemployed, what I'm learning, reading, programming, etc.}

